}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The model text on the device used to populate this entry is '''F5U307-BRN REV2'''. :The serial number is '''IT7B12070102602'''. "F5U307 REV:1.2/1.6mm", the '''Belkin''' logo, a FCC and CE logo, and some other stuff is silkscreened on the board. :The '''SMSC''' chips is marked with "SMSC", "USB2507-ADT", "A0726-AC16", and "8R130266D". :The board is using all '''G-LUXON''' capacitors.
The power adapter included with the device would appear to be an '''Coming Data''' CP0540 (100-240VAC ~ 50/60Hz 0.8A -> 5VDC 3.5-3.8A).
